1
00:00:01,117 --> 00:00:02,754
<i>Anteriormente
em Young Sheldon...</i>

2
00:00:02,765 --> 00:00:05,536
Sabe o Sr. Rosenbloom,
da loja de móveis

3
00:00:05,546 --> 00:00:07,177
